---
title: Cheesy Prawn & Hoki Mustard Filo Pie with Apple Garden Salad
description: Who doesn’t love a pie? We know we do and we know you’ll love this one, too. Tender hoki and prawns are gently cooked and stirred through a cheesy, veggie-packed filling. Flavoured with secret spices and encased in golden, flaky filo, this pie is sure to be a hit!
